org.cytoscape.property

Class SimpleCyProperty<P>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cytoscape.property.SimpleCyProperty<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    CyProperty<P>

    public final class SimpleCyProperty<P>
extends Object
implements CyProperty<P>
    A simple implementation of CyProperty suitable for general purpose use.

    Cytoscape Backwards Compatibility (Final Class): This class is final and therefore can't be extended by users. This means that we may add methods for minor version updates. Methods will only be removed for major version updates.
